CONTEXT: In About modal. Scout-App uses libraries behind-the-scenes. This gives credit and links to those libraries. 'node-sass' and 'chokidar' are library names and likely shouldn't be translated. Use best judgement.
en: Scout-App uses node-sass and chokidar .
da: Scout-App benytter node-sass og chokidar .
es: Scout-App usa node-sass y chokidar .
fr: Scout-App utilise node-sass et chokidar .
hu: A Scout-App node-sass és chokidar használatával működik.
it: Scout-App utilizza node-sass e chokidar .

CONTEXT: In About modal. A simple description of what the app is used for.
en: Scout-App allows you to process your .sass and .scss files into CSS without needing any knowledge of the command line.
da: Scout-App giver dig mulighed for at konvertere .sass og .scss filer til CSS uden kendskab til kommandolinjen.
de: Mit Scout-App generierst Du deine eigenen .sass und .scss-Dateien in CSS ohne Kenntnisse von Terminal/Eingabeaufforderung.
es: Scout-App le permite procesar sus ficheros .sass y .scss en CSS sin necesitar ningún conocimiento de la linea de comandos.
fr: Scout-App vous permet de traiter vos fichiers .sass et .scss en CSS sans avoir besoin de connaissances sur la ligne de commande.
hu: A Scout-App segít feldolgozni a .sass és .scss fájlokat, hogy parancssor ismerete nélkül is CSS stílusfájlt generálhassunk.
it: Scout-App ti permette di compilare il tuoi file .sass e .scss in CSS senza conoscere e utilizzare la linea di comando.
nl: Scout-App laat je .sass en .scss bestanden verwerken zonder enige kennis van de command line.
rk: This here Scout-App lets you turn your .sass and .scss files into .css files without needed no schoolin' in code or command-line nonesense.
ru: Cкаут-Aппa позволяет обрабатывать .sass и .scss файлы в CSS без использования командной строки
vi: Scout-App cho phép bạn xử lý các tệp .sass và .scss thành CSS mà không cần kiến thức về dòng lệnh.
zh-CHT: 無須任何命令列指令, Scout-App 幫你自動轉換 .sass 和 .scss 代碼至 CSS

When processing Sass to CSS, if there is an error in the user's Sass code, we display an alert with this as the title. 'Line' is what line of the file had the error. 'Col' is short for Column and is how many characters from the start of a line to find the error.

When the user runs a project, but its input folder doesn't have any Sass files that can be processed, this error message is displayed.

rk: Ya done goofed. You ain't got no files in your input folder.
ru: Папка ввода данного проекта не содержит файлов Sass, которые могут быть обработаны.
vi: Thư mục đầu vào của dự án này không chứa tệp Sass mà có thể xử lý được.
zh-CHT: 專案中的輸入資料夾找不到任何 Sass 檔案
